Anope 1.7.21 Fork (Xanadu IRC Services v1.0.0 Alpha)

_____________________________________________________

* Enabled the use of strlcpy instead of strcpy for handling memory.
* ChanServ Flags System added.
* Services logs are more detailed.
* ShadowIRCd 5/6.x.x protocol's added.
* HelpServ existance has been removed.
* SVSNICK and UMODE no longer requires SuperAdmin to be activated.
* AdminServ has been added.
* Built in fantasy commands.

